{
  "stem": "26111.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so it was a-- really a kind of a-- I can't say rejuvenation because it wasn't something that was there before, but a kind of inculcation of and embracing of, of Jewish forms.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, it was nothing more than forms for them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they did it largely to do me a favor--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--because it was important to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, I would say that she was-- followed more the areligious and not terribly Jewish attitudes and beliefs and emotions of my-- of my parents.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it didn't go as far as that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a gradual process, I would say.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He always had been a difficult problem.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he became a much more difficult problem after the Olympic Games were over.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The foreigners had gone home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he had to do-- Hitler had to do something to, to impress the, the populace.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what, what mainly-- the way I saw it, mainly-- the way it affected me, mainly-- is that I saw a multiplication of the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the, the-- not billboards, the display cases that were put up all over the city with the pages of the which was the anti-Semitic-- it was a publication.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think it was weekly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't think it was daily-- weekly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was-- its purpose was to show the-- to warn the populace against how horrible the Jews are, and how they must hate them, and how un-German they are, and, and how good Germans, the readers, are, in other words, Jew-hating, Jew-baiting of the worst kind.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "All Jews that were illustrated in the drawings had rather hook noses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They vastly exaggerated features, et cetera, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "All of them were leering at blond German maidens.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
